                     Audio Access to Commission Meetings

    The CPUC provides audio access to its regularly scheduled commission
     meetings (a schedule of meetings for the current year is available
     online).  Audio Access is available via your telephone or over the
                                  internet.

                               Dial-In Access

Commission Meetings

   Listen-only phone access is provided for the Commission's
   regularly-scheduled Commission meetings by dialing :   1-(877)345-0241
   - passcode 92105   (note:  continuation or specially called meetings
   will have a different phone number for which a special announcement
   will be posted).

Media Briefings

   The phone number for the listen-only access to the Commission media
   briefing is assigned on a meeting-by-meeting basis.  We will post the
   number below when a briefing has been scheduled.
     * The media briefing number is:

Webcast

     Regularly scheduled commission meetings will be broadcast over the
    internet.  The broadcast will go live approximately 10 minutes before
                     the meeting is scheduled to begin.

   If you would like to connect to the webcast or would like to access our
     archived copies of previous meetings, please visit our webcast home
                                    page.


